first_ability_desc: Has a 30% chance of inflcting either paralysis poison or sleep on attacking Pokemon on contact.
second_ability_desc: Causes 1/8 max HP in damage each turn during strong sunlight but heals for 1/8 max HP during rain. Increases damage from fire moves to 1.25X but absorbs water moves healing for 1/4 max HP.
hidden_ability_desc: Prevents self-destruct explosion and ability:aftermath from working while the Pokemon is in battle.
